description:
Think you've got skills in the kitchen?

Well, Lorraine Pascale and Jason Atherton will be the judge of that, as they co-host our brand new competitive cookery show My Kitchen Rules.

The format, which is already a big hit in Australia, will pit couples from England, Ireland, Scotland and Wales against each other in a series of cook-offs in their homes to see who can whip up the most mouth-watering menu.




My Kitchen Rules UK - Series 1, Episode 7.

How good is the the food truck in the Aussie series.

I doubt the UK series will reach this level. But it is only their first series.
